課程概述 Course Description
       代數拓樸運用代數工具來處理拓樸問題。這門課是代數拓樸的入門課，探討同倫論與同調論。題材包括基本群、覆疊空間、奇異同調、相對同調、胞腔同調、切除以及Mayer-Vietoris序列。若時間允許，將涵蓋上同調及龐加萊對偶性。Algebraic topology uses algebraic tools to study topological problems. In this introductory course, we discuss homotopy theory and homology theory. Topics include fundamental groups, covering spaces, singular homology, relative homology, cellular homology, excision, and Mayer-Vietoris sequences. If time permits, we will cover other topics such as cohomology and Poincare duality.    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives    
	    掌握代數拓樸的基礎知識和基本理論
 
 


